SUMMARY:Disability Support Hour
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Disability Support Hour at the SRJC Disability Cu
 ltural Center. This is a welcoming space for disabled students and allies
  to connect\, share experiences\, ask questions\, and build community.&#1
 60\;  Whether you're looking for peer support\, conversation\, or just a 
 place to be among others who understand\, you're invited to stop by and b
 e part of the DCC community.The DCC is on the third-floor landing in the 
 Bertolini Student Center.  For any additional access needs or questions\,
  please send us an email at srjcdcc@santarosa.edu (mailto:srjcdcc@santaro
 sa.edu)&#160\;  Visit the DRD website here! (https://drd.santarosa.edu/dc
 c)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join us for Disability Support Hour at 
 the SRJC Disability Cultural Center. This is a welcoming space for disabl
 ed students and allies to connect\, share experiences\, ask questions\, a
 nd build community.&#160\;</p><p>  Whether you're looking for peer suppor
 t\, conversation\, or just a place to be among others who understand\, yo
 u're invited to stop by and be part of the DCC community.</p><p><strong>T
 he DCC is on the third-floor landing in the Bertolini Student Center.</st
 rong></p><p>  For any additional access needs or questions\, please send 
 us an email at <a href="mailto:srjcdcc@santarosa.edu">srjcdcc@santarosa.e
 du</a>&#160\;</p><p>  Visit the <a href="https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc" t
 arget="_blank" rel="noopener">DRD website here!</a></p>
