SUMMARY:Second Chance Annual Art Show
DESCRIPTION:Please join us for the Second Chance Annual Art Show. This ev
 ent celebrates our students' creativity and highlights the power of art t
 o challenge stigma surrounding justice-impacted individuals.  Event Detai
 ls:  Date: Tuesday\, April 14\, 2026  Time: 11:00 AM – 1:00 PM  Locatio
 n: SRJC Student Activities Center (SAC)  Free parking is available in the
  Mendocino Avenue lot behind My Friend Joe Coffee. No parking tickets wil
 l be issued in this lot during the event.  All are welcome to stop by\, v
 iew the artwork and enjoy some food and light refreshments.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Please join us for the Second Chance An
 nual Art Show. This event celebrates our students' creativity and highlig
 hts the power of art to challenge stigma surrounding justice-impacted ind
 ividuals.<br />  Event Details:<br />  Date: Tuesday\, April 14\, 2026<br
  />  Time: 11:00 AM – 1:00 PM<br />  Location: SRJC Student Activities 
 Center (SAC)</p><p>  Free parking is available in the Mendocino Avenue lo
 t behind My Friend Joe Coffee. No parking tickets will be issued in this 
 lot during the event.<br />  All are welcome to stop by\, view the artwor
 k and enjoy some food and light refreshments.</p>
