 ship opportunities with you. Come to Lounibus Hall on the Santa Rosa Camp
 us between 11:00-1:30 to network! Bring your resume and be prepared to di
 scuss your career goals\, skills and what you are seeking for employment 
 or an internship.  For more information and to register\, visit SRJC's Ca
 reer Hub website! (https://careerhub.santarosa.edu/SpringUp2026)
