  and be prepared to discuss your career goals\, skills and what you are s
 eeking for employment or an internship.</p><p>  For more information and 
 to register\, visit <a href="https://careerhub.santarosa.edu/SpringUp2026
 " target="_blank" rel="noopener">SRJC's Career Hub website!</a></p>
