SUMMARY:Petaluma Cinema Series - Sirāt
DESCRIPTION:The Petaluma Cinema Series is a film education program that b
 rings together SRJC film students\, the campus community\, and Sonoma Cou
 nty residents to engage in dialogue around classic\, foreign\, &amp\; ind
 ependent films. Presentations feature SRJC film faculty\, industry guests
 \, interdisciplinary experts\, and technical demonstrations. All evenings
  include post-screening discussions.Pre-film program: 6pm  Film screening
 : 7pm (longer run times begin at 6:30pm)  Post-screening discussion until
  10pm    For more information\, visit: https://petalumafilmalliance.org/c
 inema-series/ (https://petalumafilmalliance.org/cinema-series/)&#160\;
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The Petaluma Cinema Series is a film ed
 ucation program that brings together SRJC film students\, the campus comm
 unity\, and Sonoma County residents to engage in dialogue around classic\
 , foreign\, &amp\; independent films. Presentations feature SRJC film fac
 ulty\, industry guests\, interdisciplinary experts\, and technical demons
 trations. All evenings include post-screening discussions.</p><ul><li>Pre
 -film program: 6pm  </li><li>Film screening: 7pm (longer run times begin 
 at 6:30pm)  </li><li>Post-screening discussion until 10pm  </li></ul><p> 
  For more information\, visit: <a href="https://petalumafilmalliance.org/
 cinema-series/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://petalumafilmallian
 ce.org/cinema-series/</a>&#160\;</p>
