SUMMARY:Talking About Abolition\, with Sonali Kolhatkar
DESCRIPTION:In a time of increased policing\, immigration crackdowns\, an
 d rising inequality\, an abolitionist understanding of the world can help
  us realize an economy built on the funding of public goods rather than h
 arsh enforcement.Visit SRJC's Intercultural Center website here! (https:/
 /intercultural.santarosa.edu/events)
