SUMMARY:Breaking Fast: Eritrean and Ethiopian Celebration
DESCRIPTION:This event is centered around honoring and celebrating Habesh
 a culture (Eritrean and Ethiopian)\, community\, traditions\, and people.
  This is a community wide event for students\, staff\, faculty\, family\,
  community members and allies. There will be food\, music\, celebration\,
  and community. Family Friendly Event! Event in collaboration with Sawubo
 na BLOC\, BSU\, QRC\, Petaluma Intercultural Center\, and SR Intercultura
 l Center.Visit SRJC's Intercultural Center website here! (https://intercu
 ltural.santarosa.edu/events)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  This event is centered around honoring 
 and celebrating Habesha culture (Eritrean and Ethiopian)\, community\, tr
 aditions\, and people. This is a community wide event for students\, staf
 f\, faculty\, family\, community members and allies. There will be food\,
  music\, celebration\, and community. Family Friendly Event! Event in col
 laboration with Sawubona BLOC\, BSU\, QRC\, Petaluma Intercultural Center
 \, and SR Intercultural Center.</p><p><a href="https://intercultural.sant
 arosa.edu/events" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Visit SRJC's Intercultur
 al Center website here!</a></p>
