SUMMARY:Artist Reception - Jerrold Ballaine: Land and Sea
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an artist reception to celebrate Northern Califor
 nia artist Jerrold "Jerry" Ballaine\, who has enjoyed a diverse and susta
 ined career\, including teaching at UC Berkeley. The reception will provi
 de a unique opportunity to engage directly with Mr. Ballaine. Kerry Loewe
 n\, Dean of Arts &amp\; Humanities\, will provide opening remarks. Artist
  and author Jack Leissring will speak on behalf of Mr. Ballaine. Light re
 freshments will be served.More information here! (https://www.pressdemocr
 at.com/events/#!/details/jerrold-ballaine-land-and-sea-art-exhibit-recept
 ion/18387688/2026-04-17T14)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  Join us for an artist reception to cele
 brate Northern California artist Jerrold "Jerry" Ballaine\, who has enjoy
 ed a diverse and sustained career\, including teaching at UC Berkeley. Th
 e reception will provide a unique opportunity to engage directly with Mr.
  Ballaine. Kerry Loewen\, Dean of Arts &amp\; Humanities\, will provide o
 pening remarks. Artist and author Jack Leissring will speak on behalf of 
 Mr. Ballaine. Light refreshments will be served.</p><p><a href="https://w
 ww.pressdemocrat.com/events/#!/details/jerrold-ballaine-land-and-sea-art-
 exhibit-reception/18387688/2026-04-17T14" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
 More information here!</a></p>
