SUMMARY:Petaluma Butter & Egg Days Parade and Festival
DESCRIPTION:SRJC Petaluma is excited to once again participate in the Pet
 aluma Butter &amp\; Egg Days Parade!  We're looking forward to the tradit
 ion\, fun\, and lighthearted spirit  that make this hometown celebration 
 so special.  Get ready to step into a world of wonder at the 43rd Annual 
 Butter &amp\; Egg Day Parade in Petaluma!  2026 Theme: "America's Birthda
 y - Petaluma Style"  Celebrating 250 years of independence\, ingenuity\, 
 and small-town pride.  For more information\, visit their website here! (
 https://petalumadowntown.com/butter-eggs-parade.html)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  SRJC Petaluma is excited to once again 
 participate in the Petaluma Butter &amp\; Egg Days Parade!<br />  We're l
 ooking forward to the tradition\, fun\, and lighthearted spirit<br />  th
 at make this hometown celebration so special.</p><p>  Get ready to step i
 nto a world of wonder at the 43rd Annual Butter &amp\; Egg Day Parade in 
 Petaluma!<br />  2026 Theme: "America's Birthday - Petaluma Style"<br /> 
  Celebrating 250 years of independence\, ingenuity\, and small-town pride
 .</p><p>  For more information\, <a href="https://petalumadowntown.com/bu
 tter-eggs-parade.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">visit their website
  here!</a></p>
