SUMMARY:2026 Spring Fashion Show
DESCRIPTION:The SRJC Fashion Studies Program is excited to present our an
 nual Spring Fashion Show\, a celebration of the talent and creativity of 
 our students.  This year's theme "The Equinox" is inspired by the moment 
 when night and day stand in balance\, presenting fashion as a dialogue be
 tween opposites\; structure and freedom\, rebellion and hope\, darkness a
 nd radiant color.Doors open at 7pm and the runway show begins at 7:30pm.F
 or more information and tickets\, visit the SRJC's Fashion Studies websit
 e! (https://fashion.santarosa.edu/event/spring-2026-fashion-show)
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  The SRJC Fashion Studies Program is exc
 ited to present our annual Spring Fashion Show\, a celebration of the tal
 ent and creativity of our students.</p><p>  This year's theme "The Equino
 x" is inspired by the moment when night and day stand in balance\, presen
 ting fashion as a dialogue between opposites\; structure and freedom\, re
 bellion and hope\, darkness and radiant color.</p><p><strong>Doors open a
 t 7pm and the runway show begins at 7:30pm.</strong></p><p><a href="https
 ://fashion.santarosa.edu/event/spring-2026-fashion-show" target="_blank" 
 rel="noopener">For more information and tickets\, visit the SRJC's Fashio
 n Studies website!</a></p>
