SUMMARY:Lavender Prom
DESCRIPTION:Come celebrate the end of the academic year and make unforget
 table memories at a dance hosted by Queer Resource Center\, Petaluma feat
 uring DJ and Drag Show.  Lavender Prom 2026 is an event by Queer Resource
  Center Petaluma where students and community can come and enjoy a night 
 of dancing to cap off the end of the academic year!  There will be a DJ a
 nd a special drag performer guest to keep the energy going throughout the
  night!Visit SRJC's Petaluma Intercultural Center website here! (https://
 petaluma.santarosa.edu/petaluma-intercultural-center)
