 year and make unforgettable memories at a dance hosted by Queer Resource 
 Center\, Petaluma featuring DJ and Drag Show.</p><p>  Lavender Prom 2026 
 is an event by Queer Resource Center Petaluma where students and communit
 y can come and enjoy a night of dancing to cap off the end of the academi
 c year!</p><p>  There will be a DJ and a special drag performer guest to 
 keep the energy going throughout the night!</p><p><a href="https://petalu
 ma.santarosa.edu/petaluma-intercultural-center" target="_blank" rel="noop
 ener">Visit SRJC's Petaluma Intercultural Center website here!</a></p>
