 ood Empire Food Bank prior to the event.</p><p>  Don't forget to bring yo
 ur own grocery bags\, some will be provided on a first come first serve b
 asis.</p><p>  Can't make it? Leftover produce and other items are moved t
 o the Welcome &amp\; Connect Center after each event.</p>
