 "noopener">Register here!</a></p><p>  For more information\, visit the <a
  href="https://dream.santarosa.edu/workshops-events-2025-2026" target="_b
 lank" rel="noopener">SRJC Undocu • Immigrant • Dream Center Website</
 a></p>
