DESCRIPTION:Therapy Dog Wellness Hours at the Disability Cultural Center 
  Need a moment to de-stress\, smile\, and soak up some puppy love this sp
 ring? Come join us for Therapy Dog Wellness Hours at the SRJC Disability 
 Cultural Center!  Spend time with certified therapy dogs\, enjoy their ca
 lming energy\, and leave feeling a little more grounded and recharged.Eve
 nt details:Disability Cultural Center    Santa Rosa Campus\, Bertolini St
 udent Center\, 3rd Floor Landing  12–1 PM  Free and open to all SRJC st
 udents\, staff\, and community members!    Visit the DCC Website here (ht
 tps://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc)!
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p><strong>Therapy Dog Wellness Hours at the
  Disability Cultural Center</strong></p><p>  Need a moment to de-stress\,
  smile\, and soak up some puppy love this spring? Come join us for Therap
 y Dog Wellness Hours at the SRJC Disability Cultural Center!</p><p>  Spen
 d time with certified therapy dogs\, enjoy their calming energy\, and lea
 ve feeling a little more grounded and recharged.</p><p><strong>Event deta
 ils:</strong></p><ul><li>Disability Cultural Center<br />    Santa Rosa C
 ampus\, Bertolini Student Center\, 3rd Floor Landing  </li><li>12–1 PM 
  </li><li>Free and open to all SRJC students\, staff\, and community memb
 ers!  </li></ul><p>  Visit the <a href="https://drd.santarosa.edu/dcc" ta
 rget="_blank" rel="noopener">DCC Website here</a>!</p>
